        "details": "Details\nThe scheme \"Subsidy for the Purchase of Fiber-reinforced Plastic Cattamaran/ Vallam/ Wooden Nava/ Marine Plywood Canoe With Nets\" is a Sub-Component under the Umbrella Scheme \"Financial Assistance for Availing Subsidy Components for the Development of Marine Fisheries\" by the Department of Fisheries and Fishermen Welfare, Government of Puducherry. The scheme is introduced with the objective of increasing marine fish production by extending subsidies to the fishermen for the procurement of fiber-reinforced plastic vallam with nets.",
