        "details": "Details\nUnder this scheme, a pension amount is given to all the divorced, widowed or abandoned women of Rajasthan so that they can easily bear the expenses of their house. The objective of the scheme is to provide financial help to women so that they do not face difficulties in leading a normal life.",
