        "eligibility": "Eligibility\nThe applicant's age should be 18 years or more.\nA native of the Rajasthan state.\nA widow/abandoned/divorced woman who does not have any source of regular income of her own for subsistence. (or)\nAnnual income from all sources should be less than Rs. 48,000/-."
