        "link": "https://www.myscheme.gov.in/schemes/nsfpgs",
        "details": "Details\nThe National Scholarship for Post-Graduate Studies (NSPG) scheme was established by the Ministry of Education, Government of India. The scheme was initially launched with the aim of providing financial assistance to meritorious students from economically weaker sections of society to pursue postgraduate studies in India. ",
