        "eligibility": "Eligibility\nApplicant must be pursuing first postgraduate degree. \nApplicant who have already completed a postgraduate degree are not eligible to apply.\nApplicant must be enrolled in first year of postgraduate program.\nApplicant must be under 30 years old.\nApplicant must be enrolled in full-time program.\nApplicant must be pursuing recognized postgraduate degree program."
