        "eligibility": "Eligibility\nBonafide Resident of Rajasthan. \nLess than 35 years of age on 1st July 2023\nAdmitted / Obtained offer letter in top 150 World QS ranked Universities as of 1st April, 2023\nAll disciplines for UG, PG, PhD and Post Doc courses.\nMaximum 7.5 % seats ( 37 ) for Engineering, Architecture, Medical, Dentistry courses at UG level"
