        "details": "Details\nLabor Department of Chhattisgarh State started this scheme \"Safai Karmakar Bahay Rogi Chikitsa Sahayata Yojana\" for unorganized worker on  11 March 2015. The main objective of the scheme to empower unorganized worker by providing required financial assistance for medical situation.",
