        "benefits": "Benefits\nFinancial assistance provided according to the below table\n\nClasses Boy Student  (Annual Scholarship amount) Girl Student (Annual Scholarship amount)\nClass I to V \u20b9 1,000/- \u20b9 1,500/-\nClass VI to VIII \u20b9 1,5000/- \u20b9 2,000/-\nClass IX to XII \u20b9 2,000/- \u20b9 3,000/-\nGraduation (BSc, B.Com, Diploma etc \u20b9 5,000/- \u20b9 6,000/-\nPost-Graduation ( MA, MSc, M.Com) \u20b9 7,000/- \u20b9 8,000/-\nPursuing graduate level professional course \u20b9 10,000/- \u20b9 11,000/-\nStudying for professional level, doing PhD or research work \u20b9 14,000/- \u20b9 15,000/-",
