        "name": "Scheme For Welfare Of Children In Need Of Care And Protection",
        "link": "https://www.myscheme.gov.in/schemes/swcncp",
        "details": "Details\n\"Scheme for Welfare of Children in Need of Care and Protection\" is a Social Welfare Scheme by the Directorate of Women & Child Development, Govt. of Goa. The objective of this scheme is to assist the Voluntary Organizations that cater to the needs of destitute and orphans up to the age of 18 years. To apply, the Voluntary Organizations should approach the Directorate of Women & Child Development, Panaji, Goa.",
        "benefits": "Benefits\nFinancial Assistance (Grants)\n\u20b9 400/- per child per month, if the children are housed on their own premises.\n\u20b9 500/- per child per month, if the children are housed in rented premises.",
