        "eligibility": "Eligibility\nThe applicant/pilgrim should be a permanent resident of the Haryana State.\nThe applicant/pilgrim should complete the Yatra through the State Govt./Central Govt./Society and the completion certificate in this regard must be submitted by the State/Central Govt./Society.\nFinancial assistance shall be given only once to a pilgrim."
