        "details": "Details\nChhattisgarh state Government started a scheme \"Vishvakarma Durghatana Mrtyu Par Antyeshti Evan Anugrah Raashi Bhugataan Yojana\" for labor workers. Under this scheme, benefits will be provided to the workers and their family members. \nThe main objective of starting the scheme is to provide financial help to the workers of the state. If any accident happens to a worker while working, then he or his family members are provided financial assistance under this scheme.",
